&lt;/embed&gt;
&lt;/object&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Herbert Yang</dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2014 10:19:00 -0700</pubDate><guid>tag:guizishanren.com,2014-03-10:hiking-joseph-d-grant-county-park-east-bay</guid><category></category></item><item><title>Herbert's Guide to Hawaii The Big Island</title><link>http://guizishanren.com/Herbert-Guide-Hawaii-The-Big-Island</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Hawaii is a place worth of repeated visits. It is not meant to be consumed in only one trip. I've been to Hawaii twice. The first trip was on the The Big Island. In my view this is the best of Hawaii, for its live volcano, otherworldly terrain, hidden valley, and awe-inspiring fjords. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Time of visit: August 2009&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Where are the top attractions?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/gankyun/14305377712" title="Herbert Guide to The Big Island by herbertyang, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img src="https://farm4.staticflickr.com/3672/14305377712_3f7fc3f6ab.jpg" width="800" alt="Herbert Guide to The Big Island"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;What are the top attractions?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mt. Mauna Kea, watching sunset and stargazing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;晓月坠，宿云微
&lt;a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/gankyun/3893830462" title="晓月坠，宿云微 by herbertyang, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img src="https://farm4.staticflickr.com/3508/3893830462_51d52640de_z.jpg" width="800" alt="晓月坠，宿云微"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;千里茫茫若梦
&lt;a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/gankyun/3893040625" title="千里茫茫若梦 by herbertyang, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img src="https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2520/3893040625_94efa0e3e5_b.jpg" width="800" alt="千里茫茫若梦"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;崖高人远
&lt;a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/gankyun/3893028993" title="崖高人远 by herbertyang, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img src="https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2524/3893028993_c7e957aa69_b.jpg" width="800" alt="崖高人远"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pu'u 'O'o, watching lava flow into ocean live&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;今古河山无定据
&lt;a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/gankyun/3892989333" title="今古河山无定据 by herbertyang, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img src="https://farm4.staticflickr.com/3509/3892989333_d653315d61_b.jpg" width="800" alt="今古河山无定据"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Helicopter ride, viewing The Big Island from the sky&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;剑气碧烟横
&lt;a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/gankyun/3891701925" title="剑气碧烟横 by herbertyang, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img src="https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2592/3891701925_4f68500a28_b.jpg" width="800" alt="剑气碧烟横"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;衰草连天无意绪
&lt;a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/gankyun/3893772084" title="衰草连天无意绪 by herbertyang, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img src="https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2659/3893772084_5871d97285_b.jpg" width="800" alt="衰草连天无意绪"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kilauea Iki Trail, walking through volcano crater&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hiking on Lava
&lt;a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/gankyun/3893176927" title="Hiking on Lava by herbertyang, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img src="https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2463/3893176927_212e26ae85_b.jpg" width="800" alt="Hiking on Lava"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;草木连天人骨白
&lt;a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/gankyun/3893139067" title="草木连天人骨白 by herbertyang, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img src="https://farm4.staticflickr.com/3422/3893139067_046df4f802_b.jpg" width="800" alt="草木连天人骨白"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Waipi'O Valley, hiking to the hidden paradise&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;秋雨晴时泪不晴
&lt;a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/gankyun/3893793954" title="秋雨晴时泪不晴 by herbertyang, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img src="https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2431/3893793954_1732ce2f79_b.jpg" width="800" alt="秋雨晴时泪不晴"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;悄立雁门
&lt;a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/gankyun/3892996925" title="悄立雁门 by herbertyang, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img src="https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2509/3892996925_9d3d517534_b.jpg" width="800" alt="悄立雁门"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Herbert Yang</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 01 Sep 2009 08:20:00 -0700</pubDate><guid>tag:guizishanren.com,2009-09-01:Herbert-Guide-Hawaii-The-Big-Island</guid><category></category></item></channel></rss>